            <p style="font-size:2em;text-align:center;"><b>July 16-18</b> &mdash; Morrill&nbsp;Hall, University of Nebraska State Museum</p>
            <p style="font-size:1.4em;text-align:center;">Join us in person or online to celebrate the legacy of a pioneering woman of science</p>
