               <p style="font-size:1.4em;">Those who want to write to Mary Lou and talk about their personal histories with her are welcome to do so. We will collate them into a readable, printed volume for her. Please email Scott at: <a href="mailto:slg@unl.edu">slg@unl.edu</a></p>
               <p style="font-size:1.4em;">In honoring the pioneering woman of science that she is, we have put together a program focused firmly on the future.</p>
